; Shinohara 1993; 
<bibRefCitation author="Shinohara, A. &amp; Lee, J. - W." box="[498,756,1330,1357]" pageId="76" pageNumber="77" pagination="213 - 220" refId="ref78505" refString="Shinohara, A. &amp; Lee, J. - W. (1997) Collection records of pamphiliid sawflies (Hymenoptera) from Korea. Bulletin of the National Science Museum, Tokyo, Series A, 23, 213 - 220." type="journal article" year="1997">Shinohara &amp; Lee 1997</bibRefCitation>
